These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, snowmobile, motorbike
3 different games are played: chess, canasta, bridge
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, reading, skydiving
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, designer, mechanic
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, d&b, dubstep
3 different pets are kept: hamster, horse, cat
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, aristoff, swisher
 1. the oliveros-smoker is the owner of the horse##1
 2. the swisher-smoker is the mechanic##1
 3. the person driving the motorbike is between the owner of the cat and the person driving the snowmobile##2
 4. the fan of d&b is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 5. the designer is the person playing bridge##1
 6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the owner of the hamster##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 8. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the fan of country##1
 9. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the designer##1
10. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Transport      | snowmobile    | motorbike   | ship           |
| Game          | canasta       | bridge    | chess         |
| Hobby         | reading    | skydiving  | hiking        |
| Job           | accountant | designer   | mechanic      |
| Music-Genre   | d&b        | dubstep    | country       |
| Pet   | horse     | hamster  | cat       |
| Cigar         | oliveros     | aristoff | swisher |

