.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-2::.
City: new-york, hannover, berlin
There 3 different types of food: apricot, nectarine, pear
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, disaster
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, van, jet-ski
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, british, dutch
3 different games are played: bridge, monopoly, mah-jongg
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, may, november
 1. the person playing mah-jongg is the british##1
 2. the person playing mah-jongg is the person watching disaster movies##1
 3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person traveling to hannover and the person traveling to new-york##2
 5. the dutch is on the far left##1
 6. the person traveling to hannover is the person driving the trike##1
 7. the person driving the van is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 8. the person eating apricot is the person watching adventure movies##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
10. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person eating pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| City      | new-york   | berlin    | hannover         |
| Food          | apricot    | nectarine | pear          |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure  | disaster  | animation     |
| Transport   | jet-ski       | van      | trike         |
| Nationality   | dutch      | british   | australian    |
| Game           | bridge        | mah-jongg      | monopoly         |
| Birthday         | may | april  | november |

