House: cottage, art-deco, wooden
3 different pets are kept: hamster, hedgehog, mouse
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, may, august
 1. the person eating kale is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 2. the wooden house is the person traveling to boston##1
 3. the person watching adventure movies is the person eating peas##1
 4. the person watching satire movies is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 6. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 7. the person traveling to colone is between the art-deco house and the alhambra-smoker##2
 8. the art-deco house is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
10. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person eating kale##1
11. the art-deco house is the person eating peas##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
