3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, blend, dannemann
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian, malaysian
There 3 different types of food: cherry, asparagus, peas
 1. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is the malaysian##1
 3. the person eating peas is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 4. the blend-smoker is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
 5. the dunhill-smoker is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person drinking almond-milk##2
 6. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
 7. the dunhill-smoker is the person who likes lavender##1
 8. the musician is the person eating peas##1
 9. the person drinking milk is between the musician and the social-worker##2
10. the malaysian is on the left of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |       3       |
