.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-17::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, tea
There are 3 different favourite colors: green, red, grey
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, poppy, zinnia
There are 3 different nationalities: american, indonesian, polish
3 different pets are kept: bird, fish, guinea-pig
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, ambient, house
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, alhambra, game
 1. the fan of house is in the middle##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
 3. the polish is on the right of the person who likes green##1
 4. the person who likes grey is the person who growspoppy##1
 5. the blend-smoker is on the right of the polish##1
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
 7. the game-smoker is between the person drinking almond-milk and the american##2
 8. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
 9. the person who growspoppy is the blend-smoker##1
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
11. the blend-smoker is the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | fanta      | tea      |
| Color         | green     | red     | grey  |
| Flower   | zinnia | balloon-flower  | poppy |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | polish     | american |
| Pet           | bird        | guinea-pig | fish     |
| Music-Genre         | reggae    | house | ambient   |
| Cigar     | alhambra        | game        | blend   |

