5. the oliveros-smoker is between the musician and the person who's hobby is singing##2
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
8. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
9. the person playing whist is on the left of the dressmaker##1

